quran[4{c,v,t}:
5,6,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum namaz ke liye utho to chahiye ke apne mun aur haath kohniyo-n taq dho lu, siro-n par haath phair lu aur paontalkhno-n taq dho liya karo agar janabat ki haalat mein ho to neha kar pak ho jao agar bemaar ho ya safar ki haalat mein ho ya tum mein se koi shakhs rafa haajat kar ke aeye ya tum ne aurton ko haath lagaya ho, aur pani nah miley, to pak matti se kaam lau, bas uss par haath maar kar apne mun aur hathon par phair liya karo Allah tum par zindagi ko tang nahi karna chahta, magar woh chahta hai ke tumhe pak kere aur apni Nemat tum par tamam kar day, shayad ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
5,7,"Allah ne tum ko jo Nemat ataa ki hai is ka khayaal rakho aur uss pukhta ehad o Paiman ko nah bhulo jo uss ne tum se liya hai, yani tumhara yeh qoul ke,"" hum ne suna aur itaat qubool ki"" Allah se daro, Allah dilon ke raaz taq jaanta hai"
5,8,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! Allah ki khatir raasti par qaim rehne walay aur insaaf ki gawahi dainay walay bano kisi giroh ki dushmani tum ko itna mushtael nah kar day ke insaaf se phir jao Adal karo, yeh khuda tarsi se ziyada munasbat rakhta hai Allah se dar kar kaam karte raho, jo kuch tum karte ho Allah uss se poori terhan bakhabar hai"
5,9,"jo log imaan layein aur naik amal karen, Allah ne un se wada kya hai ke un ki khataon se dar guzar kya jaye ga aur inhen bara ajar miley ga"
